 line-height: 36px; text-indent: 36px; font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial, Helvetica, 黑体, Arial, Tahoma; white-space: normal; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);\">Flow Turbulence and Combustion</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: justify; line-height: 36px; text-indent: 36px; font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial, Helvetica, 黑体, Arial, Tahoma; white-space: normal; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);\">International Journal of Heat and Fluid Flow</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: justify; line-height: 36px; text-indent: 36px; font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial, Helvetica, 黑体, Arial, Tahoma; white-space: normal; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);\">Transactions of the Japan Society for Aeronautical and Space Sciences</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: justify; line-height: 36px; text-indent: 36px; font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial, Helvetica, 黑体, Arial, Tahoma; white-space: normal; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);\">HKIE Transactions</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: justify; line-height: 36px; text-indent: 36px; font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial, Helvetica, 黑体, Arial, Tahoma; white-space: normal; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);\">Advances in Applied Mathematics and Mechanics</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: justify; line-height: 36px; text-indent: 36px; font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial, Helvetica, 黑体, Arial, Tahoma; white-space: normal; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);\">以及国内数个学报编委</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: justify; line-height: 36px; text-indent: 36px; font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial, Helvetica, 黑体, Arial, Tahoma; white-space: normal; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);\">国际学术委员会：</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: justify; line-height: 36px; text-indent: 36px; font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial, Helvetica, 黑体, Arial, Tahoma; white-space: normal; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);\">国际航空科学大会（ICAS）</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: justify; line-height: 36px; text-indent: 36px; font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial, Helvetica, 黑体, Arial, Tahoma; white-space: normal; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);\">国际湍流剪切流学术会议（TSFP）</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: justify; line-height: 36px; text-indent: 36px; font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial, Helvetica, 黑体, Arial, Tahoma; white-space: normal; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);\">国际计算流体力学学术会议（ICCFD）</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: justify; line-height: 36px; text-indent: 36px; font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial, Helvetica, 黑体, Arial, Tahoma; white-space: normal; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);\">国际湍流传热传质学术会议（THMT）</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: justify; line-height: 36px; text-indent: 36px; font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial, Helvetica, 黑体, Arial, Tahoma; white-space: normal; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);\">国际工程湍流模拟与测量学术会议（ETMM）</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: justify; line-height: 36px; text-indent: 36px; font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial, Helvetica, 黑体, Arial, Tahoma; white-space: normal; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);\">国际雷诺平均/大涡模拟混合方法学术会议（HRLM）</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: justify; line-height: 36px; text-indent: 36px; font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial, Helvetica, 黑体, Arial, Tahoma; white-space: normal; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);\">亚太国际宇航技术学术会议（APISAT）等委员会委员</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: justify; line-height: 36px; text-indent: 36px; font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial, Helvetica, 黑体, Arial, Tahoma; white-space: normal; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);\">主办第四届<a href=\"http://www.hrlm-4th.org/4th-symposium-on-hybrid-rans-les-methods/\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(114, 26, 150); text-decoration-line: none;\">HRLM</a>会议</p></div><div class=\"xq-title wow fadeInUp\" style=\"visibility: hidden; animation-name: none;\">研究领域</div><div class=\"jl-txt wow fadeInUp\" style=\"visibility: hidden; animation-name: none;\"><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: justify; line-height: 36px; text-indent: 36px; font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial, Helvetica, 黑体, Arial, Tahoma; white-space: normal; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);\">流动稳定性、转捩、湍流模式和航空工程中的空气动力学问题；湍流模式理论、湍流数值模拟与应用。</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: justify; line-height: 36px; text-indent: 36px; font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial, Helvetica, 黑体, Arial, Tahoma; white-space: normal; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);\">近年来致力于航空航天领域的流体力学研究，成立了“航空技术中心” 、“清华－GE推进与动力技术研究中心”和 “清华－沈阳飞机设计研究所联合研究中心”。</p></div><div class=\"xq-title wow fadeInUp\" style=\"visibility: hidden; animation-name: none;\">科研项目</div><div class=\"jl-txt wow fadeInUp\" style=\"visibility: hidden; animation-name: none;\"><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: justify; line-height: 36px; text-indent: 36px; font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial, Helvetica, 黑体, Arial, Tahoma; white-space: normal; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);\">自然科学基金重点项目：叶轮机械流动转捩与分离控制研究，基于混合非结构网格求解NS方程的一致高阶数值方法研究，快速几遍湍流的模式理论、数值模拟与实验研究，可压缩横向流动转捩模式研究；</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: justify; line-height: 36px; text-indent: 36px; font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial, Helvetica, 黑体, Arial, Tahoma; white-space: normal; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);\">欧洲项目：在<a href=\"http://cordis.europa.eu/project/rcn/91185_en.html\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(114, 26, 150); text-decoration-line: none;\">ATAAC</a>项目中，发展并将高精度CFD方法——混合方法应用到<a href=\"http://link.springer.com/article/10.1007/s11433-011-4601-9\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(114, 26, 150); text-decoration-line: none;\">非定常流动模拟</a></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: justify; line-height: 36px; text-indent: 36px; font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial, Helvetica, 黑体, Arial, Tahoma; white-space: normal; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);\">中欧合作项目：在<a href=\"http://cordis.europa.eu/project/rcn/96625_en.html\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(114, 26, 150); text-decoration-line: none;\">MARS</a>项目中，采用混合方法研究分离流控制和减阻方案；在<a href=\"http://cordis.europa.eu/project/rcn/110641_en.html\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(114, 26, 150); text-decoration-line: none;\">GRAIN 2</a>项目中，为绿色航空技术中的大涡模拟研究提供预研方案；</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: justify; line-height: 36px; text-indent: 36px; font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial, Helvetica, 黑体, Arial, Tahoma; white-space: normal; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);\">企业合作：与中国商飞、Airbus、美国GE航空发动机公司和日本IHI公司等开展科研合作；</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: justify; line-height: 36px; text-indent: 36px; font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial, Helvetica, 黑体, Arial, Tahoma; white-space: normal; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);\">及国家重大工程、国家重大科技专项相关项目。</p></div><div class=\"xq-title wow fadeInUp\" style=\"visibility: hidden; animation-name: none;\">奖励与荣誉</div><div class=\"jl-txt wow fadeInUp\" style=\"visibility: hidden; animation-name: none;\"><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: justify; line-height: 36px; text-indent: 36px; font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial, Helvetica, 黑体, Arial, Tahoma; white-space: normal; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);\">第五届中国青年科技奖、第四届“中国青年科学家奖”提名奖、“全国模范教师”、国际吸气式发动机学会（ISABE）“国际学术交流贡献奖”。</p></div><div class=\"xq-title wow fadeInUp\" style=\"visibility: hidden; animation-name: none;\">学术成果</div><div class=\"jl-txt wow fadeInUp\" style=\"visibility: hidden; animation-name: none;\"><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: justify; line-height: 36px; text-indent: 36px; font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial, Helvetica, 黑体, Arial, Tahoma; white-space: normal; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);\">1. <a href=\"http://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S0376042112000851\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(114, 26, 150); text-decoration-line: none;\">Fu S</a>, Wang L. RANS modeling of high-speed aerodynamic flow transition with consideration of stability theory. Progress in Aerospace Sciences, 58(201